condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, para 7 | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that the GuiGuang Railway Line iscommissioned for operation no later than December 31, 2015. | Due Date :31-Dec-2015

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, para A.2. | Description :For Section 5.08(c)of the General Conditions, the report on theexecution of the Project and related plan required shall be furnished to the Bank not later than June 30, 2016. | Due Date:30-Jun-2016

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, para B.2. | Description :The borrower shall prepare and furnish not later than 45 daysafter the end of each calendar semester, interim un-audited financialreports for the project covering the semester. | Frequency:Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, para B.3. | Description :The Borrower shall have its Financial Statement audited inaccordance with Section 5.09(b) of the General Conditions, and submit not later than six (6) months after the end of such period. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, para. A.1. | Description :The Borrower shall, within 45 days of the end of each calendarsemester furnish to the Bank a Project Report covering progress in each semester. | Frequency :Yearly
